How to setup Atom for this project..

usefull packages:
  ├── atom-beautify
  ├── atom-css-comb
  ├── atom-html-preview
  ├── color-picker
  ├── file-type-icons
  └── teletype

hint1:
  in index.html file --> to open webbrowser for realtime changes type:
    └── CTRL + SHIFT + H

hint2:
  to make teletype work:
    ├── on github: setting->developer settings->personal access tokens->generate token
    ├── click teletype icon -> copy token here
    ├── join or generate portal ID
    └── collaborate with others on one file at one moment
